data.description: Welcome to the charming double-lot (driveway has own legal address/legal description)property located just minutes away from downtown San Antonio. This exceptional offering boasts not one, but two fully renovated homes (separate electric and gas meters!), providing ample space and endless possibilities.   The main house, features three bedrooms and two bathrooms, ensuring comfort. Step inside to discover a thoughtfully designed interior that seamlessly blends modern upgrades with classic charm. The open-concept living area creates a warm and inviting ambiance, perfect for both entertaining guests and relaxing evenings.  Adjacent to the main house, the casita (currently operating as AIRBNB)  offers a unique living arrangement. This delightful one-bedroom, one-bathroom dwelling is an ideal space for guests, in-laws, or even as a lucrative rental opportunity. The casita features a spacious layout, including a generous bathroom and a convenient kitchenette, providing a comfortable and private living experience.  Location is key, and this property delivers on that front. Enjoy the convenience of living just a stone's throw away from downtown San Antonio, with its vibrant cultural scene, delectable dining options, and exciting entertainment venues. With easy access to major highways, commuting to work or exploring other parts of the city is a breeze.
